Hydras snarled at the ice surronding him. Hovering off the ground he spun 
around his swords and flames destorying and evaporating the ice around him. 
He transformed into his two headed dragon mode. This enormous form was 
incredibly quick for its size. He flew up into the air and shot flames from 
bout heads.
